# BioPolymer1_Chain

variable T equal 500.0
dimension 3
boundary p p p
atom_style full
units real

pair_style   lj/cut/coul/long 10
pair_modify   mix arithmetic #
bond_style   harmonic
angle_style   harmonic
dihedral_style   opls
improper_style   cvff
special_bonds   amber
# There 3 coefficients (a,b,c) a: 1-2 atom pair reaction, b: 1-3 reaction, c: 1-4 reaction
# The amber keyword sets the 3 coefficients to 0, 0, 1/2 for LJ interactions and to 0, 0, 5/6 for Coulombic interactions.
# The charmm keyword sets the 3 coefficients to 0, 0, 0 for both LJ and Coulombic interactions.
kspace_style pppm 1.0e-4
# A value of 1.0 means include the full interaction; a value of 0.0 means exclude it completely.
neighbor  2.0 bin
# It can be repeated if needed.
neigh_modify every 1 delay 0 check yes

read_data NCN.data

variable mytemp equal temp

#Obligation 

thermo 1000
#thermo_style    custom step temp press pe ke etotal lx ly lz pxx pyy pzz
dump            myDump all atom 2000 N3M_re_135.dump

#Equilibration Stage
minimize 1.0e-4 1.0e-6 100 1000
# etol fol maxiter maxeval

fix 1 all nvt temp $T $T 100.0 # 100.0: check the temperature
fix 2 all langevin $T $T 10.0 153
#fix_modify 2 temp newT

timestep 1.0
#fs
run 100000

write_data NCN.data

print "All Done"